<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV83">
<l>maṭṭulāvu taṇṭuḻāya laṅkalāypo laṉkaḻal</l>
<l>viṭṭuvīḻvi lātapōkam viṇṇiṉaṇṇi yēṟiṉu</l>
<l>meṭṭiṉōṭi raṇṭeṉuṅka yiṟṟiṉālma ṉantaṉaik</l>
<l>kaṭṭivīṭi lātuvaitta kātaliṉpa mākumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O You with the garland of cool tulasi where honey spreads!</l>
<l>Even if [I] go up to heaven and reach indestructible enjoyment</l>
<l rend="indent">By giving up [Your] golden feet,</l>
<l>Will [it] be [like] the unparting bliss of love [derived from]</l>
<l>Tying up the manas with the rope that is eight and two (= pattu = bhakti).</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
